{"word":"Peter","slug":"peter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Peter</b> Called Simon Bar-Jona and Cephas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=19'>Mat 16:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mar 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=42'>Joh 1:42</a><br/> A fisherman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=18'>Mat 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=7'>Luk 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=3'>Joh 21:3</a><br/> Call of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=20'>Mat 4:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=18'>Mar 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=11'>Luk 5:11</a><br/> His wife's mother healed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=14'>Mat 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=30'>Mar 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=38'>Luk 4:38</a><br/> An apostle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=2'>Mat 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=19'>Mat 16:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mar 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=14'>Luk 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a><br/> An evangelist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=37'>Mar 1:37</a><br/> Confesses Jesus as Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=19'>Mat 16:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=29'>Mar 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=20'>Luk 9:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=69'>Joh 6:69</a><br/> His presumption:<br/> - In rebuking Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=23'>Mat 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=33'>Mar 8:33</a> <br/> - When the throng was pressing Jesus and the woman of infirmity touched Him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=45'>Luk 8:45</a> <br/> - In refusing to let Jesus wash his feet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=11'>Joh 13:11</a> <br/> Present:<br/> - At the healing of Jairus' daughter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=37'>Mar 5:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=51'>Luk 8:51</a> <br/> - At the transfiguration<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=4'>Mat 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=6'>Mar 9:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=33'>Luk 9:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=18'>2Pe 1:18</a> <br/> - In Gethsemane<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=46'>Mat 26:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=42'>Mar 14:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=46'>Luk 22:46</a> <br/> Seeks the interpretation:<br/> - Seeks the interpretation:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=41'>Luk 12:41</a> <br/> - Of the law of forgiveness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=21'>Mat 18:21</a> <br/> - Of the law of defilement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=15'>Mat 15:15</a> <br/> - Of the prophecy of Jesus concerning His second coming<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=13&verse=4'>Mar 13:4</a> <br/> Walks upon the water of the Sea of Galilee<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=31'>Mat 14:31</a><br/> Sent with John to prepare the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=8'>Luk 22:8</a><br/> Calls attention to the withered fig tree<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=11&verse=21'>Mar 11:21</a><br/> His perfidy foretold by Jesus, and his profession of fidelity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=35'>Mat 26:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=31'>Mar 14:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=34'>Luk 22:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=38'>Joh 13:38</a><br/> Cuts off the ear of Malchus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=51'>Mat 26:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=47'>Mar 14:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=50'>Luk 22:50</a><br/> Follows Jesus to the high priest's palace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=58'>Mat 26:58</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=54'>Mar 14:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=54'>Luk 22:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=15'>Joh 18:15</a><br/> His denial of Jesus, and his repentance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=75'>Mat 26:75</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=72'>Mar 14:72</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=62'>Luk 22:62</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=18'>Joh 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=27'>Joh 18:27</a><br/> Visits the sepulcher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=12'>Luk 24:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=6'>Joh 20:6</a><br/> Jesus sends message to, after the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=7'>Mar 16:7</a><br/> Jesus appears to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=34'>Luk 24:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=5'>1Co 15:5</a><br/> Present at the Sea of Tiberias when Jesus appeared to His disciples; leaps into the sea, and comes to land when Jesus is recognized; is commissioned to feed the flock of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=23'>Joh 21:23</a><br/> Abides in Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a><br/> His statement before the disciples concerning the death of Judas, and his recommendation that the vacancy in the apostleship be filled<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=22'>Act 1:22</a><br/> Preaches at Pentecost<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=40'>Act 2:40</a><br/> Heals the impotent man in the portico of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3'>Act 3</a><br/> Accused by the council; his defense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=23'>Act 4:23</a><br/> Foretells the death of Ananias and Sapphira<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=11'>Act 5:11</a><br/> Imprisoned and scourged; his defense before the council<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=42'>Act 5:42</a><br/> Goes to Samaria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=14'>Act 8:14</a><br/> Prays for the baptism of the Holy Ghost<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=18'>Act 8:18</a><br/> Rebukes Simon, the sorcerer, who desires to purchase like power<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=24'>Act 8:24</a><br/> Returns to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=25'>Act 8:25</a><br/> Receives Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=18'>Gal 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=9'>Gal 2:9</a><br/> Visits Lydda; heals Aeneas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=34'>Act 9:34</a><br/> Visits Joppa; dwells with Simon, the tanner; raises Dorcas from the dead<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=43'>Act 9:43</a><br/> Has a vision of a sheet containing clean and unclean animals<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=16'>Act 10:16</a><br/> Receives the servant of the centurion; goes to Caesarea; preaches and baptizes the centurion and his household<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10'>Act 10</a><br/> Advocates, in the council of the apostles and elders, the preaching of the gospel to the Gentiles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=18'>Act 11:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=11'>Act 15:11</a><br/> Imprisoned and delivered by an angel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=19'>Act 12:19</a><br/> Writes two epistles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Pe 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=1'>2Pe 1:1</a><br/> Miracles of<br/> <a href='S:Miracles'>Miracles</a>"}]}